Helm chart refactoring: several core services were migrated from wire-server subcharts into the umbrella chart templates (`charts/wire-server/templates`).

Moved as core services:
- `background-worker`
- `brig`
- `cargohold`
- `galley`

As a result, dependency tags for moved services are obsolete for the current wire-server chart, because these services are no longer resolved through `requirements.yaml` dependencies. In particular, `tags.brig`, `tags.galley`, and `tags.cargohold` are no longer needed for wire-server deployments.
